{ This quiet continuation will forever damage Black's kingside pawn structure. }
16. Qb3 Rxd5 17. Ne4 f5 { This is why ...gxf6 is preferred over ...Bxf6. } 18.
Qb2 { 18.Ng3  b6  19.Nh5!?  Can be investigated further. } 18... Rf8 19. Ng3 b6
