24. Rd8+ Bxd8 25. Qxe4 Rxa6 26. Qb4
{ We restrict Black from castling and furthermore prevent the rooks from connecting. White should have some practical chances in this endgame due to this reason. Once Black's pieces are activated, the position should equalize, but that is easier said than done. }
