18... Qxb2 19. Qxe4 O-O 20. Be5 Qb4 { Only move. Otherwise White takes on g6. }
21. Qxb4 Bxb4 22. Rd7 { Getting the rook on the 7th rank. } 22... Rf7 23. Rxf7
Kxf7 24. Rb1 { The other rook joins the party! } 24... a5 25. c3 Be7 26. Rb7
{ With a fantastic endgame ahead. The rook is on the 7th rank, the bishop is on the best possible square, it couldn't get better than this! }
