Bxd6 24. Rxd6+ Kc8 25. Ra8+ { We have more material to take! } 25... Kc7 26.
Rd7+ Kb6 27. Rxh8
{ The position has calmed down now, and even though Black has a queen, White has more than enough material along with beautifully placed pieces, the kingside pawns will be taken soon enough. }
