{ Black gets the bishop out early. The reader should note that there is a small difference in comparison to the variation with  2...Nf6  3.e3  Bf5  as in that variation the knight has committed itself to ...f6. The majority of the lines here will transpose to that chapter, but there are some cases where it does not. I will explain this shortly. }
