{ On the other hand, creates an imbalance in the form of an IQP, this can be utilized in the long run with }
15. Nb3 Bb6 16. Rfd1
{ Controlling the d4-square so that Black is not able to push ...d4. } 16...
Rfd8 17. Qb5 { With the idea of a4 next. } *

