12... cxd4 13. exd4 Re8 14. Bf4
{ Prophylactic move aimed against ...e5. White wants to take and reroute the London bishop to e3, where it will put pressure on the b6-pawn.   14.Nc3  is also fine.  14...Ne4  15.Nxe4  Bxe4  16.Qd2  with the idea of a5. }
14... Ne4 15. Be3 e5 16. dxe5 dxe5 17. a5
{ And White will eventually take on b6, which makes the c4-pawn quite dangerous. }
