Nd7 17. Nf3 Ne5
{ It should be noted that  17...O-O-O  is always going to be dangerous because of  18.cxb4  since the c-file remains open.  18...cxb4  19.Nxg5+-  And White is dominating. }
18. Nxe5 Bxe5 19. Bxg5
{ The material is equal, the position is not. Black's problems are far from resolved. The king remains in dangerous territory, the rooks will struggle to develop, the queen is completely out of play. }
