[FEN "rnbqk2r/pp3ppp/4pn2/8/2NP4/5N2/PP1Q1PPP/R3KB1R w KQkq - 0 11"]
[SetUp "1"]

{ This game is an example from two extremely strong players in their prime. Arjun found a rather simple move here that gives him a winning position. White to play. }
11. Qb4 { Not allowing Black to castle and threatening Nd6+. } 11... Qe7 12.
Nd6+ Kf8 13. Ne5 { With complete dominance. Black resigned in a few moves. } *

[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
