[SetUp "1"]

{ White has managed to generate a kingside attack, but the h5-knight restricts us from going further. How did White continue here? }
17. Bh2 { Sacrificing the h-pawn and going for g4 next. } 17... Bxh4 18. g4 Ng7
19. Bf4 { With a completely winning position thanks to the open h-file. } *

[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
