[SetUp "1"]

{ In this position, Nihal played  9.O-O  and allowed  9...Ne4!  which equalized the position. Can you find a better move? }
9. Bc2
{ An extremely clever move in anticipation of ...Ne4.  9.O-O  Ne4  10.Nxd7  Qxd7=  Happened in the game. }
9... Ne4 10. f3 Nxd2 11. Qxd2 f6 12. Qd3
{ The point behind Bc2. Now Black is forced to play  12...f5  after which White can go  13.O-O-O  and demolish Black on the kingside. }
*

[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
[Date "????.??.??"]
