[SetUp "1"]

{ Once again, we reach a position where Black has done all the right things. How should White continue? }
16. cxd5 exd5 17. dxc5 bxc5 18. Ba6
{ The point behind the exchange. Nihal realizes that without the b7-bishop, the hanging pawns become a target. }
18... Rac8 { 18...Bc6=  was the best response. } 19. Bxb7 Qxb7 20. b3
{ With lasting play against the hanging pawns. } *

[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
