{ The knight on h5 looks a bit awkward. How should White continue? } 8. g4 Nf6
9. g5 Ne4
{ 9...Nh5??  would have finished the game sooner rather than later with  10.Nh4+- }
10. Bxg7 { With an extra pawn. } *

