{ We have already seen this motif before. How should White continue? } 13. a5
b5 14. c4 bxc4 15. Nxc4 Qb8 16. Nfd2
{ Getting the knight out of the f3-square so the queen can be activated. }
16... Bd5 17. Bf1 { Protecting g2. White is ready to go Qa4 next. } *

[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
