[SetUp "1"]

{ Black has just played ...f6 to simplify the position and take control over the e5-square. How should White continue? }
11. Nxc6 Qxc6 12. Qc2
{ Important move. White puts pressure on the e4-knight to provoke ...f5, which inevitably gives up the e5-square. }
12... f5 13. Bxd6 Nxd6 14. Ne5 { With a great position. } *

[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
[Date "????.??.??"]
