[SetUp "1"]

{ Another similar example of the same position. Since the queen is on c7, the move should be clear for White. }
14. c4 a5
{ Black does not allow a5 anymore, but, gives up control over the b5-square. }
15. Nb1 Qd8 16. Nc3
{ The position is complicated, but White has much easier play because of the b5-square. }
