[Result "*"]
[FEN "r1q2rk1/4bpp1/p1n1pnp1/1p1p4/3P1B2/2PQ1N1P/PP1N1PP1/R3R1K1 w - - 0 16"]
[SetUp "1"]

{ Black is preparing for a queenside launch, perhaps via ...Qb7-a5 and either ...b4 or ...a4. How can we put a stop to this plan and gain control over the queenside? }
16. b4
{ Thematic principle. Gaining control over the outpost on c5 and preparing for a4 next. This idea is quite common in the carlsbad structure with reversed colours. }
16... Nd7 17. a4
{ With the idea of Nb3-Nc5. The computer also seems to like the a5 push @@StartBracket@@if Black allows it@@EndBracket@@ and afterwards go Nb3-Nc5 and start the kingside attack via h4. }
