[SetUp "1"]

{ The knight on a5 seems a bit misplaced at the moment, but if White does nothing, then ...Nc4 becomes a problem in the future. How does White continue? }
16. Ne5 { Controlling the c4-square. } 16... b5
{ Black is adamant on getting ...Nc4. Time for action! } 17. h4
{ Preparing for a kingside attack. } 17... Nc4 18. Ndxc4
{ 18.Rab1  was played in the game where Black could have equalized with  18...Nxd2  19.Bxd2  Ne4= }
18... bxc4 19. Qh3
{ The queenside is now more or less closed. White's kingside attack has only begun. Threats like g4-h5 are quite dangerous. }
*

[Event "?"]
