[SetUp "1"]

{ White's position looks fantastic. How did Nihal breakthrough to win this game? }
19. b4 { Opening up the c-file. } 19... cxb4 20. axb4 Nf8 21. Nc8 Ra4 22. Ne7+
Kh7 23. Ne5
{ With a dominating position. The idea is to go Rc7 and of course, take on f7. }
