[SetUp "1"]

{ Black played ...a4 to open up the a-file. How can White make sure this does not happen? }
21. b4
{ The b4-pawn is poisoned!  21.Rfe1  happened in the game where Black managed to equalize after  21...axb3  22.axb3=  However, Nihal managed to win the game at the end. }
21... Qb6 22. a3 { The weakness on c6 will be taken soon. } *

