[SetUp "1"]

{ Once again, we reach a french-like position where things have not been going great for Black. The kingside is lacking pieces at the moment. This might be the right moment to go for the attack! }
11. h4 { Threatening the greek gift. } 11... f5 12. exf6 Nxf6 13. Ne5
{ Black's pawn on e6 is vulnerable. White has dominance over the e5-square. The idea should be to go O-O soon and play against these two weaknesses. }
