[SetUp "1"]

{ This is a fairly common position where Black's knight on h5 is temporarily misplaced. How should White take advantage of this? }
8. dxc5 Bxc5
{ Black does not allow the e4-break. Fortunately, there is a backup plan!  8...Qxc5  allows the simple  9.e4⩲ }
9. b4 { Kicking the bishop. } 9... Be7
{ 9...Bd6?!  can be met with  10.Nc4±  With a great position. } 10. b5
{ The point. Black is forced to give up castling. } 10... h6 11. Bh4 Na5 12.
Bxe7 Kxe7 13. Qa4
{ Threatening Qb4+ next, with the idea of g4-g5 sometime soon. } *

[Event "?"]
