{ The opening has gone perfectly for White. Could this be the right time to go for the kill? }
13. Bxe4 dxe4 14. Ng5 h6
{ 14...Nf6  allows  15.Ng4+-  and Black is dead lost. } 15. Nxe6 { The point. }
15... fxe6 16. Qxe6+ Kh7 17. Nxd7 { And White is completely winning. } *

[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
